<!-- Repair Costs and About Section -->
<section class="repair-costs-about-section">
  <div class="repair-costs-about-wrapper">
    <div class="repair-costs-about-container">
      <!-- Repair Costs Section -->
      <div class="costs-section-inner">
        <h2 class="section-title">Lawn mower repair costs in Denver</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Compare average pricing across verified shops in the Denver area.</p>
        <div class="costs-grid">
          <div class="cost-card">
            <div class="cost-card-main">
              <div class="cost-icon">
                <%= image_tag "blade-sharpening-icon.svg", alt: "Blade Sharpening", class: "cost-icon-img" %>
              </div>
              <div class="cost-card-content">
                <h3 class="cost-service">Blade Sharpening</h3>
                <p class="cost-price">$10 - $25</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="cost-description">Per blade; balance included</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cost-card">
            <div class="cost-card-main">
              <div class="cost-icon">
                <%= image_tag "basic-tuneup-icon.svg", alt: "Basic Tune-up", class: "cost-icon-img" %>
              </div>
              <div class="cost-card-content">
                <h3 class="cost-service">Basic Tune-up</h3>
                <p class="cost-price">$60 - $120</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="cost-description">Oil, filter, spark plug, blade</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cost-card">
            <div class="cost-card-main">
              <div class="cost-icon">
                <%= image_tag "carburetor-cleaning-icon.svg", alt: "Carburetor Cleaning", class: "cost-icon-img" %>
              </div>
              <div class="cost-card-content">
                <h3 class="cost-service">Carburetor Cleaning</h3>
                <p class="cost-price">$45 - $90</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="cost-description">Remove, clean, reinstall</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cost-card">
            <div class="cost-card-main">
              <div class="cost-icon">
                <%= image_tag "engine-repair-icon.svg", alt: "Engine Repair", class: "cost-icon-img" %>
              </div>
              <div class="cost-card-content">
                <h3 class="cost-service">Engine Repair</h3>
                <p class="cost-price">$150 - $500</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="cost-description">Varies by issue</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cost-card">
            <div class="cost-card-main">
              <div class="cost-icon">
                <%= image_tag "belt-replacement-icon.svg", alt: "Belt Replacement", class: "cost-icon-img" %>
              </div>
              <div class="cost-card-content">
                <h3 class="cost-service">Belt Replacement</h3>
                <p class="cost-price">$40 - $120</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="cost-description">Parts and labor included</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cost-card">
            <div class="cost-card-main">
              <div class="cost-icon">
                <%= image_tag "deck-repair-icon.svg", alt: "Deck Repair", class: "cost-icon-img" %>
              </div>
              <div class="cost-card-content">
                <h3 class="cost-service">Deck Repair</h3>
                <p class="cost-price">$80 - $250</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="cost-description">Welding and restoration</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- About Section -->
      <div class="about-section-inner">
        <h2 class="section-title">About Denver Repair Services</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          Denver's lawn mower repair market offers diverse options for homeowners and commercial operators. With over 300 days of sunshine annually, Denver residents rely heavily on well-maintained lawn equipment throughout the extended growing season. The city's repair shops range from budget-friendly basic service providers to premium authorized dealers offering comprehensive warranties and mobile service. Most shops in the Denver metro area offer turnaround times between same-day to two weeks, depending on complexity and parts availability.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
